- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is likely because the paper considers operations on regular languages and finite weighted transition systems, which are topics related to formal languages and automata theory. 
- cs.THEORY (Theoretical Computer Science) is likely because the paper deals with the behaviour of systems and the specification of operations on them, which are topics related to theoretical computer science. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible because the paper deals with the behaviour of systems and the specification of operations on them, which can be seen as a type of algorithmic problem.
